git clone https://github.com/apache/logging-log4j2.git logging-log4j2-fork-apache
cd logging-log4j2-fork-apache
export JAVA_HOME_8_X64=$HOME/java/jdk8
export JAVA_HOME_11_X64=$HOME/java/jdk11
export JAVA_HOME=${JAVA_HOME_8}
Run command for "verify" in .github/workflows/build.yml, namely:
          ./mvnw \
            --show-version --batch-mode --errors --no-transfer-progress \
            -DtrimStackTrace=false \
            -Dsurefire.rerunFailingTestsCount=2 \
            -Dlog4j2.junit.fileCleanerSleepPeriodMillis=1000 \
	    -Drat.skip=true \
            --global-toolchains ".github/workflows/maven-toolchains.xml" \
            verify

This worked on godwit.
On my home computer, MongoDB 3 tests failed with
  java.lang.RuntimeException: Could not start process: <EOF>
even after I rebooted and did
  export LC_ALL=C

